    <entry>
      <title>关于Ubuntu搭建LAMP+Discuz的学习记录</title>
      <link href="/posts/43955.html"/>
      <url>/posts/43955.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>@[toc]</p><h3 id="配置ssh服务"><a href="#配置ssh服务" class="headerlink" title="配置ssh服务"></a>配置ssh服务</h3><blockquote><p>  1、修改ssh配置文件</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo vim /etc/ssh/sshd_config</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>  2、修改文件的“PermitRootLogin prohibit-password”为”PermitRootLogin yes”</p></blockquote><blockquote><p>  3、重启ssh服务，这样子就可以使用远程终端工具连接上了。</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">systemctl restart ssh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="进行必要的更新"><a href="#进行必要的更新" class="headerlink" title="进行必要的更新"></a>进行必要的更新</h3><blockquote><p>  1、更新源</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt update</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>  2、更新软件</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt upgrade -y</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="安装apache2"><a href="#安装apache2" class="headerlink" title="安装apache2"></a>安装apache2</h3><blockquote><p>  1、安装apache2</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt install apache2 -y</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>  2、在浏览器输入你的IP看到下图说明apache2安装成功</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://dms.9i7.fun/ExamplePhoto/example_4.png"></p><blockquote><p>  3、设置apache2开机自启动</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">systemctl enable apache2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>  other：apache2的其他操作</p></blockquote><table><thead><tr><th align="center">命令</th><th align="center">作用</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">systemctl start apache2</td><td align="center">开启apache2</td></tr><tr><td align="center">systemctl stop apache2</td><td align="center">关闭apache2</td></tr><tr><td align="center">systemctl restart apache2</td><td align="center">查看apache2状态</td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="安装MySQL"><a href="#安装MySQL" class="headerlink" title="安装MySQL"></a>安装MySQL</h3><blockquote><p>  1、安装MySQL</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt install mysql-server mysql-client -y</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>  2、进入MySQL</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mysql</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>  3、修改密码为Aa20030202</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ALTER USER &#x27;root&#x27;@&#x27;localhost&#x27; IDENTIFIED WITH mysql_native_password by &#x27;Aa20030202&#x27;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>  4、退出MySQL</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">exit;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>  5、初始化MySQL</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo mysql_secure_installation</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>  6、设置MySQL开机自启动</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">systemctl enable mysql</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="安装PHP"><a href="#安装PHP" class="headerlink" title="安装PHP"></a>安装PHP</h3><blockquote><p>  1、安装PHP</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt install libapache2-mod-php -y</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>  2、查看PHP版本号</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">php -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://dms.9i7.fun/ExamplePhoto/example_5.png"></p><h3 id="关联"><a href="#关联" class="headerlink" title="关联"></a>关联</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt install php-mysql -y</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install php-gd -y</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install php-curl -y</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install php8.1-xml -y</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="测试环境"><a href="#测试环境" class="headerlink" title="测试环境"></a>测试环境</h3><blockquote><p>  1、进入目录</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd /var/www/html</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>  2、创建test.php文件</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">touch test.php</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>  3、将以下内容写入文件</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span> <span class="title function_ invoke__">phpinfo</span>(); <span class="meta">?&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>  4、在浏览器输入http:&#x2F;&#x2F;你的IP&#x2F;test.php，查看网页验证是否成功</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://dms.9i7.fun/ExamplePhoto/example_6.png"></p><h3 id="安装Discuz论坛系统"><a href="#安装Discuz论坛系统" class="headerlink" title="安装Discuz论坛系统"></a>安装Discuz论坛系统</h3><blockquote><p>  1、安装zip</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt-get install zip -y</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>  2、创建目录</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mkdir /var/www/html/discuz/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>  3、安装Discuz系统</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">if [ -f /usr/bin/curl ];then curl -sSLO https://www.discuz.vip/install/X3.5.sh;else wget -O X3.5.sh https://www.discuz.vip/install/X3.5.sh;fi;bash X3.5.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>  4、重启apache2</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">systemctl restart apache2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>  5、访问http:&#x2F;&#x2F;你的IP&#x2F;discuz&#x2F;install&#x2F;，进入安装向导</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://dms.9i7.fun/ExamplePhoto/example_7.png"></p><blockquote><p>  6、按照提示完成安装</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://dms.9i7.fun/ExamplePhoto/example_8.png"></p><p>到这里Ubuntu搭建LAMP+Discuz就完全成功啦！</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
